{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b53fb86e5","title":"邓小平与胡耀邦谈起草在中央工作会议闭幕会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0894f839cb","index":0,"year":1978,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"2b53fb86e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"8ea55d34c1","name":"胡耀邦","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e18872b239","type":"title","text":"邓小平与胡耀邦谈起草在中央工作会议闭幕会上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"809dbf4857","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"d7a5e1cdfc","type":"appellation","text":"〖胡耀邦、于光远等人为邓小平起草在中央工作会议闭幕会上的讲话，邓小平与胡、于谈话，指示摘录如下。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"1cae19bb4e","type":"paragraph","text":"讲过了，与外国人讲过。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"a976b5fcf0","type":"paragraph","text":"究竟讲什么，想了一下，不准备长稿子。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"d9796dc8c6","type":"subtitle","text":"（谈对中央工作会议的评价）","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"13ea6995c9","type":"paragraph","text":"这次会议了不起，五七年以后没有（五七年以前有，延安有，那时议论问题自然一些）。这个风气要传下去，很好的党的生活，党的作风，既有利于安定团结，防止思想僵化，又有利于……实在可喜。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"f0eaad563d","type":"subtitle","text":"（关于解放思想）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"3e08cace51","type":"paragraph","text":"这个争论（即真理标准的讨论──引者注）很好，越看越好，是政治问题，是国家命运问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"2cb2dc5739","type":"subtitle","text":"（关于发扬民主加强法制）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"b1141778c9","type":"paragraph","text":"在现在这个时期更要加强民主。集中多少年，现在是民主不够，不敢讲，心有余悸。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"0a89c16dae","type":"paragraph","text":"发展经济，民主选举，民主管理，民主监督。工厂工人监督，农村社员监督。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"d83741ec4d","type":"paragraph","text":"目前主要是反对空头政治……反对说空话。现在是正确的意见，也不落实，没有具体措施，一拖就是一年。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"465b2fe8be","type":"paragraph","text":"讲权力下放，企业。讲讲千方百计，讲调动积极性。利用每一寸土地，有一点土地种一棵树，有一块水面搞养殖，有一块草原种草。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"6b8826dc22","type":"subtitle","text":"（关于自主权与国家计划的矛盾）","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"79eb0712cf","type":"paragraph","text":"这个矛盾只能从价值法则供求关系来调整。……否则不能自主，靠质量，质量好销全国。不要怕，乱，乱不出来（承认市场一定调节）。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"c6fb9c5a85","type":"paragraph","text":"经济民主，重点不是政治，重点是经济民主。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"17950fd136","type":"paragraph","text":"有些要用法律，民法，刑法，各种单行法，植树应该有法律。地方也可以立法。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"1ff932b739","type":"subtitle","text":"（关于向前看）","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"176e1e192d","type":"paragraph","text":"这个会议向后看解决一些问题，目的是为了向前看，不要一刀切，解决遗留问题，快，干净利落，时间不要长。完全满意不可能。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"bf8879a163","type":"paragraph","text":"安定团结十分重要。……毛主席文化大革命中问题，不纠缠这个问题。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"99121ac9f1","type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命，不要涉及，让时间来说清，过一段时间再说这个问题，没有一点吃亏。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"5f3fd6b877","type":"subtitle","text":"（谈克服官僚主义）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"8538a4c1e7","type":"paragraph","text":"学会管理，培养与选用人才，使用人才，改革规章制度。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"376dcc9300","type":"paragraph","text":"好的企业必须用先进的办法管理企业。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"5d323abe2d","type":"paragraph","text":"党委领导好不好，看企业管得好不好，利润，工人收入，城市如此，农村如此，各行各业如此。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"91f8b61922","type":"subtitle","text":"（谈允许一部分企业、地区、社员先好起来）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"0e523e438b","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个大政策。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"cc2ca6f1f4","type":"paragraph","text":"允许一部分先富起来，农村５－１０－２０％；城市２０％，才有市场。本身就促进就开辟新行业。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"82f9d3ddbe","type":"paragraph","text":"反对平均主义。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"6cc210c934","type":"paragraph","text":"干得好的，就影响左邻右舍。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"e5bd33c01e","type":"subtitle","text":"（关于加强责任制）","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"03028ac732","type":"paragraph","text":"现在无人员责任。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"8655ab1f8a","type":"paragraph","text":"搞几定：（１）什么项目，（２）从哪里引进，（３）定在什么地方，（４）定哪个人从谈判到管理。可能六七定，开单子，并头进行，不耽误时间。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"},{"id":"c45bfa0951","type":"paragraph","text":"现在打屁股打计委，有什么用？要打，打个人。国内企业也要专人负责，专门机构、专门的人搞几定，请些专家，譬如荣毅仁就可以当专家。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5"}],"page":{"id":"c97809da2f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2b53fb86e5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}